reviews.review_text: Brent's Blues During Rider You Could See It Hit Jerry. The 2nd Set Was A Filled With Songs Of Loss Rider, L.L. Rain, He's Gone Then Into The Spoonful Jam And A Quick Taste Of New Speedway Boogies Soon To Come.  We Grieved, We Grooved And Oh How We Missed Brent's Fills And Harmonys. Watching Vince Seemingly Lost With His Mouth Agape For Minutes At A Time You Could Only Think, Bad Hire. Days Later Bruce To The Rescue. (For Awhile At Least.
